Package: db4.8-doc
Architecture: all
Section: doc
Priority: optional
Description: Berkeley v4.8 Database Documentation [html]
 This package contains documentation in HTML format for all of
 the APIs (C, C++, C#, STL, Java, Tcl) and utilities provided
 by version 4.8 of Berkeley DB.

